# Commands

Run from repo root. Node **>= 24.14.0**. Package manager: **npm**.

## Before claiming done (CI order)

1. `npm run format:check` — or `npm run format` then re-check
2. `npm run lint`
3. `npx tsc --noEmit` — no `typecheck` script yet; use this
4. `FLUENT_USER_EMAIL=test@example.com npm test -- --ci`

Report what ran and the outcome. If a step was skipped, say why.

## Development

| Command | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `npm install` | Install deps |
| `npm start` | Metro bundler |
| `npm run android` | Run on Android emulator/device |
| `npm run format` | Fix Prettier (broader than `format:check`) |

## CI mirrors

- Lint + format: `.github/workflows/lint.yml`
- Test: `.github/workflows/test.yml` (sets `FLUENT_USER_EMAIL`)
- Android build: `.github/workflows/build.yml`

## PR workflow

Slash commands in `.cursor/commands/`: `/create-pr-branch`, `/generate-pr-description`, `/create-pr`. Align with team PR title format: `[TICKET-ID]: Description`.

## Do not run without user request

- Force push, hard reset
- Commits or push (unless user asks)
- Modifying `.env` or secrets
